French Plan to Roll Over Greek Debt Depends on Rating Held Above Default

-- B y   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 
2011-06-28T15:04:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/french-plan-to-roll-over-greek-debt-depends-on-rating-held-above-default.html
A proposal by French banks to roll
over their Greek debt depends upon credit-rating firms not
cutting their grade on  Greece  and existing or newly issued
government securities to default, according to a draft of the
plan.  To contact the reporter on this story:
